data.description: Welcome to your dream home located in a prime location. This is a very desired 1 story house from Adams Homes (model 2117). This exquisite 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence offers a seamless blend of convenience, comfort, and style. Great location at the end of a cul-de-sac surrounded with beautiful conservation . As you step inside this home, you'll be greeted by a tastefully updated kitchen that's both functional and visually appealing. Spacious living areas, high ceilings, where the open layout seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making entertaining a joy. This home comes with a low HOA fee that includes Internet and Cable. Don't miss your chance to own this fantastic property that truly encapsulates the best of Florida living. With its strategic location, this is more than just a home; it's a lifestyle waiting to be embraced. All measurements are approximate.
